title: POJO for HTX, HTD, and HTT requests. See HistoricalViaTCPIP

basisForLast.title:
Possible single character values include:
C - Last Qualified Trade.
E - Extended Trade = Form T trade.
O - Other Trade = Any trade not accounted for by C or E.
S - Settle = Daily settle, only applicable to commodities.

tradeMarketCenter.title: The Market Center the trade occurred at.

tradeConditions.title: The trade conditions. Format: One to four, 2 digit hex numbers.

tradeAggressor.title:
The trade aggressor. Possible values include:
0 - Invalid (not supported).
1 - Buy.
2 - Sell.
3 - Neither buy nor sell.

dayCode.title: The day of month the trade applies to.
